title: #92Noon! Nordo in for PA! Florio/Snob/Ryan Burns
description: -- Nordo fills in for PA for the rest of the week, Pro Football Talk’s Mike Florio joins the show, Cory Cove, Meatsauce, and producer Brett Blakemore play Stump the Snob, Ryan Burns joins to talk Gopher Football, and the guys get their thoughts out on the Vikings less than stellar start to the year.
